data.description: Welcome to this lovely three-bedroom, one bathroom home sitting on almost half an acre! Spacious and inviting, as you walk through the front door you will feel right at home! An abundance of natural light fills the living room that opens to your kitchen. Enjoy the weather all year in your sunroom that looks onto your beautiful back yard. Also, offering a great amount of storage and much more. Schedule your showing today and make this house your home!MAKE THIS HOUSE YOUR HOME TODAY!!!!
